<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><text><body><div type="session" n="28"><head><supplied resp="#BF">28. Vorlesung, <ref target="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/gliederung"><date when="1828-02-09">9. Februar 1828</date></ref></supplied></head><lb/>
<div n="1"><div n="2"><p>In <choice><abbr>jed</abbr><expan resp="#TK">jedem</expan></choice> Theil <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Erde ist 20-30′ <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Temperatur<lb/>
beständig. So bei <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Luft 26° in Paris@ war in<lb/>
10′ nur 11°, 20′ <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> mittlere Temperatur 11½°.<lb/>
Weñ <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">Rotation</hi>zeit <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">den</expan></choice> ♂ <choice><abbr>zunähe</abbr><expan resp="#TK">zunähere</expan></choice>, so würde@ <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Punkt<lb/>
<choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> mittlere Temperatur näher <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Oberfläche liegen.</p><lb/>
<p>In <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">den</expan></choice> Bergwerken <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice> viele <hi rendition="#aq">Experimente</hi> gemacht von<lb/>
<hi rendition="#aq"><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-118804790 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118804790">Saussoure</persName> etc</hi>. <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> merkwürdigsten <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice> in England<lb/>
gemacht worden. <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> Luft dort zu <choice><abbr>utsuh</abbr><expan resp="#TK">untersuchen</expan></choice> ist nicht<lb/>
gut, der <choice><abbr>verschied</abbr><expan resp="#TK">verschiedenen</expan></choice> Strömungen wegen, <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Wasser@ <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice><lb/>
besser, am <choice><abbr>best</abbr><expan resp="#TK">besten</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Bohrlöcher im Gestein. So von<lb/>
<hi rendition="#aq"><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-11889448X http://d-nb.info/gnd/11889448X">Trebra</persName></hi>. Man hat <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Wärme im̃er zunehmend<lb/>
gefunden. <hi rendition="#aq"><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-117528552 http://d-nb.info/gnd/117528552">Fox</persName></hi> hat bis 20° im Iñern <choice><abbr>gefund</abbr><expan resp="#TK">gefunden</expan></choice>.<lb/>
Auf <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Höhe <choice><abbr>v</abbr><expan resp="#TK">von</expan></choice> 11000′ in <hi rendition="#aq">Peru</hi> <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>nh</abbr><expan resp="#TK">noch@</expan></choice> 15°<lb/>
<choice><abbr>gefud</abbr><expan resp="#TK">gefunden</expan></choice>, obgleich <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>mittl</abbr><expan resp="#TK">mittlere</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">Temperatur</hi> 6°-7° war<lb/>
<hi rendition="#aq"><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-102458561 http://d-nb.info/gnd/102458561">Cartier</persName></hi> hat <choice><abbr>e</abbr><expan resp="#TK">eine</expan></choice> Menge <choice><abbr>v</abbr><expan resp="#TK">von</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>dies</abbr><expan resp="#TK">diesen</expan></choice> Versuchen gemacht. <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice><lb/>
Zunahme ist <choice><abbr>v</abbr><expan resp="#TK">von</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">dem</expan></choice> Gestein <choice><abbr>u</abbr><expan resp="#TK">und</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">Local</hi> abhängig.</p><lb/>
<p>Bei 80<supplied resp="#TK"><subst><del rendition="#ow">°</del><add place="across">′</add></subst></supplied> nim̃t <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Temperatur schon 1° zu, da <choice><abbr>s</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sie</expan></choice><lb/>
bei <choice><abbr>Steig</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Steigen</expan></choice> in <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Luft <choice><abbr>bi</abbr><expan resp="#TK">bei</expan></choice> 600′ erst <choice><abbr>u</abbr><expan resp="#TK">um</expan></choice> 1° ab-<lb/>
nim̃t. <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> beßten@ Versuche <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice> in <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">dem</expan></choice> Keller <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">Observa-<lb/>
torien</hi> in Paris. 9,4° ist <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Temperatur in 80′<lb/>
<choice><abbr>dad@</abbr><expan resp="#TK">dadurch@</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>mittl</abbr><expan resp="#TK">mittlere</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">Paris</hi> 8° ist. – <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> Quellen <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice> zu<lb/>
<choice><abbr>eb</abbr><expan resp="#TK">eben</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>dies</abbr><expan resp="#TK">diesem</expan></choice> Zweck gebraucht. Einige verändern ihre<lb/>
Temperatur gar nicht, manche sehr wenig.</p><lb/>
<p><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-116817569 http://d-nb.info/gnd/116817569"><hi rendition="#aq">L.</hi> v Buch</persName> hat große Erdwärme in H.@ <choice><abbr>gefund</abbr><expan resp="#TK">gefunden</expan></choice>.<lb/>
Es giebt dort im̃er <choice><abbr>fließd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">fließende</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Quell</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Quellen</expan></choice>. <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Quelle´</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Quellen</expan></choice><lb/>
<choice><abbr>nehm</abbr><expan resp="#TK">nehmen</expan></choice> an Temperatur nach <hi rendition="#aq">H</hi> im̃er zu, in Italien<lb/>
ist <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Temperatur <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Quell</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Quellen</expan></choice> geringer als <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Luft.<lb/>
<persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-118554700 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118554700">Humboldt</persName> hat dasselbe gefunden. <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> Ursache<lb/>
ist <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Regenzeit, <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> in <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>niedigst</abbr><expan resp="#TK">niedrigsten</expan></choice> Temperatur<lb/>
<choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">dem</expan></choice> Wasser geben. <del rendition="#s">Auch</del> <choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Der</expan></choice> Schnee dient@ hierzu<lb/>
in <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">dem</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Nord</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Norden</expan></choice>, da <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Ausström</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Ausströmung@</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Wärme verhindert,<lb/>
<del rendition="#s">nicht</del> mal@ <choice><abbr>ab</abbr><expan resp="#TK">aber</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> Luft in <choice><abbr>ihr</abbr><expan resp="#TK">ihrer</expan></choice> Temperatur ändert.<lb/>
<choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> Eismasse im Iñern <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Erde <choice><abbr>v</abbr><expan resp="#TK">von</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq"><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-11903705X http://d-nb.info/gnd/11903705X">Gmelin</persName></hi> angeblich<lb/>
<choice><abbr>gefund</abbr><expan resp="#TK">gefunden</expan></choice> in 100′. <hi rendition="#aq">Cap <persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-118692844 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118692844">Franklin</persName></hi> hat neuerdings<lb/>
in 3′ Tiefe Eismasse <choice><abbr>gefund</abbr><expan resp="#TK">gefunden</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>bi</abbr><expan resp="#TK">bei</expan></choice> 65½° <hi rendition="#aq">Br</hi>.<lb/>
<choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> ￼ <choice><abbr>Quell</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Quellen</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>sd</abbr><expan resp="#TK">sind</expan></choice> wärmer, als <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">die</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>andr</abbr><expan resp="#TK">anderen</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>dabiliegnd@</abbr><expan resp="#TK">dabeiliegenden@</expan></choice>.<lb/>
<choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Die</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>ausgebreitet</abbr><expan resp="#TK">ausgebreiteten</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">Vulcane</hi> <choice><abbr>geb</abbr><expan resp="#TK">geben</expan></choice> sehr viel ￼</p><lb/>
