<div n="3"><p><hi rendition="#u">Magnetismus</hi>. <hi rendition="#aq"><persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-118847767 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118847767">Arago</persName>s</hi> Versuch, daß <hi rendition="#u">alle</hi> <choice><abbr>Körp</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Körper</expan></choice> <hi rendition="#aq">tran-<lb/>
sitorisch</hi> <choice><abbr>Magnetsm@</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Magnetismus</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>annehm</abbr><expan resp="#TK">annehmen</expan></choice>, <hi rendition="#u">alle</hi> Nadeln schwingen<lb/>
langsam <choice><abbr>bi</abbr><expan resp="#TK">bei@</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Nähe aller Körper. <persName resp="#SB" ref="http://www.deutschestextarchiv.de/kosmos/person#gnd-116461357 http://d-nb.info/gnd/116461357">Hansteen</persName><lb/>
beobachtet <choice><abbr>bi</abbr><expan resp="#TK">bei</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Bäum</abbr><expan resp="#TK">Bäumen</expan></choice> <del rendition="#s">in</del> Pole in <choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Länge und in<lb/>
<choice><abbr>d</abbr><expan resp="#TK">der</expan></choice> Breite. –</p></div></div></div></div></body></text></TEI>